			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://revivalmedia.org/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/russb.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1242" title="russbravo" src="http://revivalmedia.org/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/russb.jpg" alt="russbravo" /></a>Welcome to the final Weekly News Review from a Christian Viewpoint.  Patrick Woodward talks to <strong>Russ Bravo</strong>, (pictured) editor of <a onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/outbound/article/www.inspiremagazine.org.uk');" href="http://www.inspiremagazine.org.uk/default.aspx" target="_blank">Inspire Magazine,</a> about the latest news from a Christian standpoint.  Today, as snow blankets the south, why does everything stop? A new survey of religious beliefs highlights decline in Christianity, and a Christmas sermon in 160 characters.</p>
